_sText:
Hey! Good to see you found my map...

Some tips for first timers:
1. Surf Clockwise around the rings.
2. Brown ramps push you out, white ramps push you inward.
3. Behind the brown blocks up top are secret areas. ;)
4. There is no way out of jail, except death.
5. The sides of the platforms in jail teleport to each other.

ENJOY!!!
~Chaos Theory~

Change log from beta3:
1. Changed a few textures in the Ring area.
2. Changed / Optimized jail lighting.
3. Removed the fences in the Ring area.
4. Added some lamps and lights for nice effects.
